properties.Name: CustomerCountryOfResidence
properties.Description:
The country of residence of the customer as of the associated time.

This answers the question "What country(s) does the individual have residence for?"

Columns.Name: CustomerId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Customer.

Columns.Name: CountryId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the Country.

Columns.Name: PeriodStartDate
Columns.Description: The period start date that the customer has residency in the associated country.

Columns.Name: PeriodEndDate
Columns.Description: The period end date that the customer has residency in the associated country.

Columns.Name: CountryResidencyStatusId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Country Residency Status.

Columns.Name: ResidencePermitVisaId
Columns.Description: The identifier of 'number' of the residence permit or visa associated with residence in the associated country.
